title: Unspecified error occurred. please check the logs for more information(HELP)
body:
I get this error while starting the installation on my MacBook. I want to be able to play while I'm not at home at my PC. What do I do? DNS-change didn't work. Using Google's atm and still doesn't work. 

Anyone with a solution?

replies.body: This might be happening if that Mac doesn't have the right admin settings in place for League to run. These work a little differently on Macs than Pc's, but you can find some steps to walk you through it on this guide over here -> [**Mac Admin Rights**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664#mq9)

I tried everything on that page, I still get the same message. WHAT DO I DO? :(
I want some ARAMs.

Let's go ahead and get you a little more in-depth help from one of our tech guys to figure out what might be going wrong here. Hit them up in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and they'll be able to take a look at your system and logs to see if anything looks out of place.
